window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Drift into peaceful slumber with the soothing sounds of Italy's Amalfi Coast, captured in stunning Dolby Atmos surround sound.</p> <p>This immersive soundscape, recorded on location, offers a tranquil auditory journey perfect for bedtime relaxation. Let the gentle lapping of Mediterranean waves against the shore wash away the day's stress. The soft, rhythmic sounds create a natural white noise that helps calm your mind and prepare your body for sleep. Experience the subtle rustling of lemon tree leaves in a light coastal breeze, enveloping you in a cocoon of calming coastal sounds, helping to block out disruptive noises and create an ideal environment for restful sleep.</p> <p>Wake up feeling rejuvenated, as if you've spent the night in a Mediterranean paradise.</p> <p>Produced by Wonder Media Network.</p> <p>Available in Dolby Atmos on Audible.</p>"; 
